trans-unit.source: Represents a control that acts as a container for a group of controls within a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView" /> control.
trans-unit.target: Representa un control que actúa como contenedor de un grupo de controles contenidos en un control <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView" />.

trans-unit.source: In this topic:
trans-unit.target: En este tema:

trans-unit.source: [Introduction](#introduction)
trans-unit.target: [Introducción](#introduction)

trans-unit.source: [Declarative Syntax](#declarative_syntax)
trans-unit.target: [Sintaxis declarativa](#declarative_syntax)

trans-unit.source: Introduction
trans-unit.target: Introducción

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control is a container for a group of controls.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control es un contenedor para un grupo de controles.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control must always be contained within a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> control.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control siempre debe estar incluido dentro de un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> control.

trans-unit.source: Only one <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control at a time can be defined as the active view within a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> control.
trans-unit.target: Solo un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control a la vez puede definirse como la vista activa dentro de un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> control.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView.ActiveViewIndex%2A> property specifies the active <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control within the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView.Views%2A> collection of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> control.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView.ActiveViewIndex%2A> propiedad especifica el activo <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control dentro de la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView.Views%2A> colección de un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> control.

trans-unit.source: The active view control is rendered to the client, as long as the containing <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> control is visible.
trans-unit.target: El control de vista activa se representa en el cliente, siempre que la que contiene <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> control es visible.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Visible%2A> property to determine whether a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control and its child controls are visible on the page and rendered to the client.
trans-unit.target: Use la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Visible%2A> propiedad para determinar si un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control y sus controles secundarios están visibles en la página y se ha procesado para el cliente.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control can contain controls of any type, including other <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> controls.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> puede contener controles de cualquier tipo, incluidos otros <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> controles.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control does not support any style properties.
trans-unit.target: Un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control no admite las propiedades de estilo.

trans-unit.source: To apply styles to a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control, add one or more <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> controls to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control.
trans-unit.target: Para aplicar estilos a un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> de control, agregue uno o varios <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> controles a la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> class provides the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Activate> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Deactivate> events.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> clase proporciona el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Activate> y <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Deactivate> eventos.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Activate> event is raised when the current <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control becomes the active view.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Activate> evento se desencadena cuando actual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control se convierte en la vista activa.

trans-unit.source: This occurs when the value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView.ActiveViewIndex%2A> property changes or the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView.SetActiveView%2A> method is called to specify a different <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control.
trans-unit.target: Esto se produce cuando el valor de la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView.ActiveViewIndex%2A> cambios de propiedad o el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView.SetActiveView%2A> método se llama para especificar otro <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control.

trans-unit.source: For example, if `View1` is the active view within a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> control, when the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView.ActiveViewIndex%2A> property changes to specify `View2`, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Activate> event is raised for `View2` and the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Deactivate> event is raised for `View1`.
trans-unit.target: Por ejemplo, si `View1` es la vista activa dentro de un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> control, cuando la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView.ActiveViewIndex%2A> cambios de propiedad para especificar `View2`, el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Activate> evento se desencadena para `View2` y <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Deactivate> evento se desencadena para `View1`.

trans-unit.source: To allow users to navigate between multiple <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> controls within a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> control, you can add a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton> or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Button> control to each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control.
trans-unit.target: Para permitir que los usuarios puedan navegar entre varios <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> controla dentro de un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> (control), puede agregar un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton> o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Button> el control a cada uno de ellos <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control.

trans-unit.source: Set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton> or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Button> control's `CommandName` property to the ID of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control to navigate to.
trans-unit.target: Establecer el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton> o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Button> del control `CommandName` propiedad al identificador de la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control para navegar por.

trans-unit.source: For a code example, see <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView.ActiveViewChanged>.
trans-unit.target: Para obtener un ejemplo de código, vea <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView.ActiveViewChanged>.

trans-unit.source: For more information on manipulating <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> controls within a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> control, see the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> topic.
trans-unit.target: Para obtener más información sobre la manipulación de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> controla dentro de un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> control, vea el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> tema.

trans-unit.source: The first time the page is loaded, `DefaultView` is set as the active view.
trans-unit.target: La primera vez que se carga la página, `DefaultView` se establece como la vista activa.

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control contains link buttons to allow the user to navigate to different views.
trans-unit.target: Cada <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control contiene botones de vínculo para permitir al usuario navegar a distintas vistas.

trans-unit.source: Note that each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control contains a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> control to allow styles to be applied.
trans-unit.target: Tenga en cuenta que cada <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control contiene un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> control para permitir que los estilos que se aplicará.

trans-unit.target: Esto se produce cuando el valor de la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView.ActiveViewIndex%2A> cambios de propiedad o el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView.SetActiveView%2A> método se llama para especificar otro <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control.

trans-unit.target: Por ejemplo, si `View1` es la vista activa dentro de un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> control, cuando la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView.ActiveViewIndex%2A> cambios de propiedad para especificar `View2`, el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Activate> evento se desencadena para `View2` y <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Deactivate> evento se desencadena para `View1`.

trans-unit.source: When the active view changes, a message is displayed to the user specifying the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control that raised the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Activate> event and the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control that raised the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Deactivate> event.
trans-unit.target: Cuando la vista activa cambios, se muestra un mensaje para el usuario que especifica la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> controlar que ha provocado el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Activate> eventos y el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> controlar que ha provocado el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Deactivate> eventos.

trans-unit.source: Occurs when the current active <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View" /> control becomes inactive.
trans-unit.target: Aparece cuando el control <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View" /> activo actual se inactiva.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Deactivate> event is raised when the current active <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control becomes inactive.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Deactivate> evento se desencadena cuando el activo actual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control pasa a estar inactivo.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control becomes inactive when the value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView.ActiveViewIndex%2A> property changes or the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView.SetActiveView%2A> method is called to specify a different <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control pasa a estar inactiva cuando el valor de la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView.ActiveViewIndex%2A> cambios de propiedad o el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView.SetActiveView%2A> método se llama para especificar otro <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control.

trans-unit.source: For example, if `View1` is the active view within a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> control, when the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView.ActiveViewIndex%2A> property changes to specify `View2`, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Deactivate> event is raised for `View1` and the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Activate> event is raised for `View2`.
trans-unit.target: Por ejemplo, si `View1` es la vista activa dentro de un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> control, cuando la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView.ActiveViewIndex%2A> cambios de propiedad para especificar `View2`, el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Deactivate> evento se desencadena para `View1` y <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Activate> evento se desencadena para `View2`.

trans-unit.source: When the active view changes, a message is displayed to the user specifying the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control that raised the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Activate> event and the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control that raised the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Deactivate> event.
trans-unit.target: Cuando la vista activa cambios, se muestra un mensaje para el usuario que especifica la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> controlar que ha provocado el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Activate> eventos y el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> controlar que ha provocado el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Deactivate> eventos.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether themes apply to this control.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene o establece un valor que indica si los temas se aplican a este control.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> to use themes; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> para usar temas; en caso contrario, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The default is <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: El valor predeterminado es <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.EnableTheming%2A> property indicates whether themes are enabled for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.EnableTheming%2A> propiedad indica si los temas están habilitados para el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.EnableTheming%2A> property also affects whether themes are enabled for the controls contained in its <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Controls%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> collection.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.EnableTheming%2A> propiedad también afecta a si se habilitan los temas para los controles incluidos en su <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Controls%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> colección.

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.EnableTheming%2A> property is `true`, the application's theme directory is searched for control skins to apply.
trans-unit.target: Cuando el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.EnableTheming%2A> propiedad es `true`, directorio de temas de la aplicación se busca máscaras para los controles.

trans-unit.source: If no skin for the particular control exists in the theme directory, a skin is not applied.
trans-unit.target: Si no existe ninguna máscara para un control determinado en el directorio de temas, no se aplica una máscara.

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.EnableTheming%2A> property is `false`, the theme directory is not searched and the contents of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.SkinID%2A> property are not used.
trans-unit.target: Cuando el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.EnableTheming%2A> propiedad es `false`, no se busca en el directorio de temas y el contenido de la <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.SkinID%2A> no se utiliza la propiedad.

trans-unit.source: A control can override the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.EnableTheming%2A> value set by its parent control, or by the containing page.
trans-unit.target: Un control puede invalidar la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.EnableTheming%2A> valor establecido por su control principal o por la página que lo contiene.

trans-unit.source: For example, if a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control has <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.EnableTheming%2A> set to `false`, you can selectively apply themes to child controls contained within the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control by setting the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.EnableTheming%2A> property to `true` on the individual child controls.
trans-unit.target: Por ejemplo, si un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control tiene <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.EnableTheming%2A> establecido en `false`, puede aplicar temas selectivamente a controles secundarios que contienen el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control estableciendo la <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.EnableTheming%2A> propiedad `true` en los controles secundarios individuales.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.EventArgs" /> that contains the event data.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.EventArgs" /> que contiene los datos del evento.

trans-unit.source: Raises the <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Activate" /> event of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View" /> control.
trans-unit.target: Provoca el evento <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Activate" /> del control <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Activate> event is raised when the current <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control becomes the active view.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Activate> evento se desencadena cuando actual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control se convierte en la vista activa.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.EventArgs" /> that contains the event data.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.EventArgs" /> que contiene los datos del evento.

trans-unit.source: Raises the <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Deactivate" /> event of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View" /> control.
trans-unit.target: Provoca el evento <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Deactivate" /> del control <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Deactivate> event is raised when the current active <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control becomes inactive.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Deactivate> evento se desencadena cuando el activo actual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control pasa a estar inactivo.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View" /> control is visible.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene o establece un valor que indica si el control <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View" /> está visible.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View" /> control is visible; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: Es <see langword="true" /> si el control <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View" /> está visible; en caso contrario, es <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The default value is <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: El valor predeterminado es <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Visible%2A> property to determine whether the current <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control is visible and rendered to the client.
trans-unit.target: Use la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Visible%2A> propiedad para determinar si la actual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control es visible y se ha procesado para el cliente.

trans-unit.source: For a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control to be visible on the rendered page, it must be the active view in its containing <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> control, and the containing <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> control must be visible.
trans-unit.target: Para una <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> de control para que esté visible en la página representada, debe ser la vista activa en la que lo contiene <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> control y la que contiene <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> control debe ser visible.

trans-unit.source: If the containing <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> control is not visible on the page, or if the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control is not the active view, then the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control and its child controls are not rendered.
trans-unit.target: Si la que contiene <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MultiView> control no está visible en la página, o si la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control no es la vista activa, el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> no se representan el control y sus controles secundarios.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Visible%2A> property is set internally based on the visibility and active view for the containing parent control.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Visible%2A> propiedad se establece internamente basándose en la visibilidad y la vista activa para el control primario que lo contiene.

trans-unit.source: If you set this property at run time, an <xref:System.InvalidOperationException> exception is thrown.
trans-unit.target: Si establece esta propiedad en tiempo de ejecución, un <xref:System.InvalidOperationException> se produce la excepción.

trans-unit.source: If you set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Visible%2A> property at design time, any changes to the property are ignored.
trans-unit.target: Si establece la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View.Visible%2A> propiedad en tiempo de diseño, los cambios en la propiedad se omite.

trans-unit.source: An attempt was made to set this property at run time.
trans-unit.target: Se intentó establecer esta propiedad en tiempo de ejecución.
